dimension_like.label: Delivery Appointment Is Weekend (Yes / No)
dimension_like.name: last_delivery_appointment.is_weekend

queryResponse.sql:
SELECT
    (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('month', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(last_delivery_appointment.created_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM')) AS "last_delivery_appointment.created_month",
        (EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(last_delivery_appointment.created_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))::integer) AS "last_delivery_appointment.created_year",
        (CASE WHEN (MOD(EXTRACT(DOW FROM CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(coalesce(last_delivery_appointment.end_at::timestamp ,last_delivery_appointment.start_at::timestamp)  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))::integer - 1 + 7, 7)) in (5,6)  THEN 'Yes' ELSE 'No' END) AS "last_delivery_appointment.is_weekend",
    COUNT(DISTINCT last_delivery_appointment.id ) AS "last_delivery_appointment.shipment_stop_appointments_count"
FROM stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipments  AS shipments
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipment_stops  AS last_delivery ON last_delivery.shipment_id=shipments.id and last_delivery.last_stop and (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('second', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(last_delivery.deprecated_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS')) is null
INNER JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipment_stop_appointments  AS last_delivery_appointment ON last_delivery_appointment.shipment_stop_id=last_delivery.id and NOT ((TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(last_delivery_appointment.deprecated_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) is not null)
GROUP BY
    (DATE_TRUNC('month', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(last_delivery_appointment.created_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))),
    2,
    3
ORDER BY
    1 DESC
FETCH NEXT 500 ROWS ONLY
